2. Implement the topological sort - I'll use Kahn's algorithm or DFS-based approach. DFS is simpler:
   - Use DFS to visit all nodes
   - Keep track of visited, in-progress, and completed nodes
   - If we encounter an in-progress node during DFS, we have a cycle
   - Add node to result when we complete processing it

